      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know... it feels less like a quiet moment and more like a period at the end of a sentence. like i've read the book, i've seen the sights, and the credits are starting to roll. everything is just so heavy and i'm just... exhausted from trying to find \"magic\" in things that feel so hollow.",
